Honestly, who would give up FT III or Vengeance III to get 3 regen per tick and spell haste?? Unless you've already got FT or Vengeance maxed out, you wouldn't. Stats are nice, but no matter how high your STR or skills are, Vengeance will ALWAYS add to your ATTACK. And no matter how large your mana pool is, how fast you regen it is what really counts. <br>
<br>
